---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
		<header class="text-white relative min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-center py-16 md:py-24">
		<img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0" src="/header_bg.webp" alt="Horizons Equinox Background" />
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black via-black/83 to-transparent z-0"></div>
			
		<div class="relative z-10 w-full text-center px-4 mt-8 md:mt-12">
			<img class="w-3/4 md:w-1/2 mx-auto mb-4" src="/equinox_logo.webp" alt="Horizons Equinox Logo" />
			
			<div class="text-white">
				<h1 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-[3rem] md:leading-tight font-bold mb-2 md:mb-4">August 14-16 @ The GrEEK Campus, Cairo, Egypt</h1>
				<h2 class="font-futura text-lg md:text-3xl mt-2 font-normal">Code for 35 hours, <br class="hidden md:block" /> Get invited to a 3-day hackathon adventure</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="relative mt-8 md:mt-12 flex justify-center">
				<div class="p-0.5 rounded-full bg-[#EC7A0F]">
					<button class="font-futura text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold bg-black text-[#ec7a0f] px-8 md:px-14 py-2 rounded-full block">
						<a href="https://horizons.hackclub.com">
							get started!
						</a>
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>
		<main class="bg-black text-white px-4 pt-12 md:pt-10 pb-0 text-center relative overflow-hidden">

		<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative px-4">
            <img src="/asset4.webp" alt="ankh" class="hidden md:block absolute -left-30 top-40 w-[24%]">
			
			<p class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl leading-snug md:leading-tight mb-10 md:mb-16">
				This August, we are bringing together 80+ teen coders from all around the world to join us for a free 3-day hackathon adventure in Egypt, <b>Horizons Equinox</b>.
			</p>
			<h1 class="font-karim text-6xl md:text-[9.5rem] py-0 mb-2 md:mb-0 text-center">
				All for free!
			</h1>
			<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl leading-tight mb-12 md:mb-16">
				Free meals & snacks * Local transport * Event swag <br class="hidden md:block">
				Flight stipends available for extra hours
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 mb-16">
			<p class="font-futura text-xl md:text-4xl leading-snug md:leading-tight">
				Create something new, get to see the pyramids of Giza up-close, code with new friends, ride a cruise down the Nile, and get immersed in Egyptian culture all in the span of 3 days!
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="px-4">
			<img src="/howtoqual.webp" alt="how to qualify" class="w-full md:w-[70%] mx-auto">
		</section>

		<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-16 md:mt-20 mb-12 relative px-4">
			<h1 class="text-center font-karim text-6xl md:text-[8.5rem] mb-0 md:mb-0 leading-tight">previous events</h1>
				
			<div id="events-scroll-container" class="w-screen relative left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 overflow-x-auto snap-x snap-mandatory no-scrollbar py-4">
				
				<div id="events-track" class="flex gap-6 md:gap-12 w-max items-center">
					
					<div class="w-[92vw] sm:w-[85vw] md:w-[800px] shrink-0 snap-center flex flex-col items-center md:-rotate-2">
						<div class="w-full shadow-xl">
							<img src="counterspell.webp" alt="Counterspell" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover bg-black block" />
						</div>
						<div class="mt-2 md:mt-2 text-center px-2">
							<h3 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-2"><a href="https://counterspell.hackclub.com">Counterspell</a></h3>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="w-[92vw] sm:w-[85vw] md:w-[800px] shrink-0 snap-center flex flex-col items-center md:rotate-2">
						<div class="w-full shadow-xl">
							<img src="/shipwrecked.webp" alt="Shipwrecked" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover bg-black block" />
						</div>
						<div class="mt-2 md:mt-2 text-center px-2">
							<h3 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-2"><a href="https://shipwrecked.hackclub.com">Shipwrecked</a></h3>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="w-[92vw] sm:w-[85vw] md:w-[800px] shrink-0 snap-center flex flex-col items-center md:-rotate-2">
						<div class="w-full shadow-xl">
							<img src="outernet.webp" alt="Outernet" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover bg-black block" />
						</div>
						<div class="mt-2 md:mt-2 text-center px-2">
							<h3 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-2"><a href="https://outernet.hackclub.com">Outernet</a></h3>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="w-[92vw] sm:w-[85vw] md:w-[800px] shrink-0 snap-center flex flex-col items-center md:-rotate-2">
						<div class="w-full shadow-xl">
							<img src="/overglade.webp" alt="Overglade" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover bg-black block" />
						</div>
						<div class="mt-2 md:mt-2 text-center px-2">
							<h3 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-2"><a href="https://overglade.hackclub.com">Overglade</a></h3>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="w-[92vw] sm:w-[85vw] md:w-[800px] shrink-0 snap-center flex flex-col items-center md:rotate-2">
						<div class="w-full shadow-xl">
							<img src="/undercity.webp" alt="Undercity" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover bg-black block" />
						</div>
						<div class="mt-2 md:mt-2 text-center px-2">
							<h3 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-2"><a href="https://undercity.hackclub.com">Undercity</a></h3>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="w-[92vw] sm:w-[85vw] md:w-[800px] shrink-0 snap-center flex flex-col items-center md:-rotate-2">
						<div class="w-full shadow-xl">
							<img src="assemble.webp" alt="Assemble" class="w-full aspect-[3/2] object-cover bg-black block" />
						</div>
						<div class="mt-2 md:mt-2 text-center px-2">
							<h3 class="font-futura text-2xl md:text-5xl mb-2"><a href="https://assemble.hackclub.com">Assemble</a></h3>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<script>
			document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
				const scrollContainer = document.getElementById('events-scroll-container');
				const track = document.getElementById('events-track');
				const originalCards = Array.from(track.children);
				originalCards.forEach(card => track.appendChild(card.cloneNode(true)));
				originalCards.forEach(card => track.appendChild(card.cloneNode(true)));

				let autoScrollInterval;
				let isJumping = false;

				function getSetWidth() {
					return track.scrollWidth / 3;
				}

				requestAnimationFrame(() => {
					scrollContainer.scrollLeft = getSetWidth();
				});

				scrollContainer.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
					if (isJumping) return;

					const setWidth = getSetWidth();
					
					if (scrollContainer.scrollLeft <= setWidth * 0.5) {
						isJumping = true;
						scrollContainer.style.scrollSnapType = 'none'; 
						scrollContainer.scrollLeft += setWidth;
						
						requestAnimationFrame(() => {
							scrollContainer.style.scrollSnapType = '';
							isJumping = false;
						});
					} 
					else if (scrollContainer.scrollLeft >= setWidth * 2.5) {
						isJumping = true;
						scrollContainer.style.scrollSnapType = 'none';
						scrollContainer.scrollLeft -= setWidth;
						
						requestAnimationFrame(() => {
							scrollContainer.style.scrollSnapType = '';
							isJumping = false;
						});
					}
				});

				function startAutoScroll() {
					autoScrollInterval = setInterval(() => {
						const cardWidth = originalCards[0].offsetWidth;
						const gap = window.innerWidth > 768 ? 48 : 24; 
						
						scrollContainer.scrollBy({ left: cardWidth + gap, behavior: 'smooth' }); 
					}, 3000); 
				}

				function stopAutoScroll() {
					clearInterval(autoScrollInterval);
				}

				scrollContainer.addEventListener('mouseenter', stopAutoScroll);
				scrollContainer.addEventListener('mouseleave', startAutoScroll);
				scrollContainer.addEventListener('touchstart', stopAutoScroll, { passive: true });
				scrollContainer.addEventListener('touchend', startAutoScroll);

				startAutoScroll();
			});
		</script>

		<img src="/cats.webp" alt="Cats" class="w-[90%] md:w-3/4 mx-auto mb-6 md:mb-2" />

		<section class="bg-black text-white py-10 px-4 pt-0 relative">
			<h1 class="text-center font-karim text-6xl md:text-[8.5rem] mb-10 md:mb-8">FAQs</h1>
			<img src="/asset2.webp" class="hidden md:block absolute w-[25%] right-5 bottom-[300px]" alt="horus">
			
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 md:gap-x-16 gap-y-12 text-left">
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-y-10 md:gap-y-12">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-karim text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">What is Hack Club?</h2>
						<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
							Hack Club is a global 501(c)(3) nonprofit based in the United States built by teens to support teen coders and we’ve run 500+ hackathons and events worldwide online and in-person.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-karim text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">Who can attend?</h2>
						<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
							Teenagers aged 13–18 from any part of the world!
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-karim text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">How do stipends work?</h2>
						<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
							For each additional hour you code you get $8.5 US Dollars credits which can be used to purchase flight stipends. So if you code 20 more hours thats 20 hours x $8.5/hour = $170
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex flex-col gap-y-10 md:gap-y-12 relative">
					<div class="absolute -left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-white/20 hidden md:block"></div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-karim text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">How do I qualify?</h2>
						<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
							There are 3 simple steps:<br>
							1. Sign up via Horizons<br>
							2. Code for 35+ hours<br>
							3. You're qualified!
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-karim text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">Where can I find travel information?</h2>
						<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
							We'll have a travel guide with visa, flight and arrival/departure details added here before June :)
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-karim text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-3">I have more questions</h2>
						<p class="font-futura text-lg md:text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
							You can reach out to us via equinox@horizons.hackclub.com or have a Zoom call with one of the organisers :)
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<footer class="w-screen relative left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center mt-10">
			<img src="/asset3.webp" alt="footer decoration" class="relative z-20 w-[100%] md:w-[50%] mb-4 md:mb-8">
			
			<div class="relative w-full flex justify-center items-center pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-24 lg:pt-64 z-10">
					<img src="/footer.webp" alt="footer bg decoration" class="hidden md:block absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-[80%] md:w-[72%] lg:w-[56%] z-0 pointer-events-none object-right-bottom">
				
				<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center -mt-25 md:-mt-50 px-4">
					<p class="font-karim text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center">made with love by teens at hack club</p>
					<p class="font-futura text-sm md:text-lg mt-2 text-center text-white/80">Hack Club is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit built by teens for teens.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>

	</main>
</Layout>